 Pryzm 老板将夜店关闭归咎于“年轻人少喝酒” https://www.nme.com/news/music/pryzm-boss-blames-young-people-drinking-less-for-nightclub-closures-3588126?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pryzm-boss-blames-young-夜总会关闭导致人们少喝酒Max PilleyThu, 15 Feb 2024 21:32:44 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3588126 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="夜总会" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Banquet Records 本周证实 Pryzm 将保持营业，但英国夜总会关闭数量创历史新高</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pryzm-boss-blames-young-people-drinking-less-for-nightclub-closures-3588126">Pryzm 老板将夜总会关闭归咎于“年轻人少喝酒”，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="夜总会" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/freedom-day-nightclubs-getty-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>金斯顿 Pryzm 的老板表示，英国夜总会普遍关闭的原因之一是“年轻人喝酒少了”。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="281" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2023-was-worst-year-for-venue-closures-while-no-one-in-music-industry-seems-to-care-say-mvt-3562266"><b>MVT 表示，2023 年是“场馆关闭最糟糕的一年”，而“音乐行业似乎没有人关心”</b></a></li></ul><p>上个月，在拥有<a href="https://www.pryzm.co.uk/">Pryzm</a>和<a href="https://www.atikclub.co.uk/">Atik</a>品牌的所有者<a href="https://rekomgroup.com/brands">Rekom UK</a>进入破产管理程序后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/owners-of-uks-pryzm-and-atik-nightclubs-call-in-administrators-3571633">，金士顿 Pryzm 的未来受到质疑</a>。该公司列举了过去一年夜间行业面临的挑战，将其问题归咎于能源价格上涨和学生因当前生活成本而削减开支。</p><p>然而，上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/banquet-records-announces-that-kingston-pryzm-is-saved-3581452">Banquet Records 证实，经常举办“户外”演出的 Kingston Pryzm</a>场地<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/banquet-records-announces-that-kingston-pryzm-is-saved-3581452">将继续开放</a>，尽管其业主已致电管理员。 </p><figure id="attachment_3571673" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3571673" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3571673" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/RekomPryzm-Atik-administration-.jpg" alt="Pryzm 夜总会的外观" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/RekomPryzm-Atik-administration-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/RekomPryzm-Atik-administration--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/RekomPryzm-Atik-administration--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/RekomPryzm-Atik-administration--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/RekomPryzm-Atik-administration--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/RekomPryzm-Atik-administration--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3571673" class="wp-caption-text">普里兹姆夜总会。图片来源：Chris Eades/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>现在，Rekon 英国首席执行官彼得·马克斯 (Peter Marks) 告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-68295306" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC</a> ，由于饮酒习惯的改变、生活成本危机和房租价格飙升，年轻人和学生的外出次数比以往任何时候都少。</p><p>他说：“许多过去每月支付 800 英镑住宿费的学生现在面临着每月 1,200 英镑的[更高租金]。” “显然，人们仍然喜欢外出，[但是]如果资金紧张，[他们]会晚点来，所以他们会晚点到达我们家门口，而且花的钱也会更少。”</p><p> “我晚上7点到11点之间走了一圈，城里的人不超过200人。两年前，这里真的非常繁忙和热闹。”</p><p> Banquet Records 定期在该场地举办亲密的专辑发行演出，并举办过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenius 等乐队的演出，</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future-islands">Future Island</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a>等乐队也计划在未来在这里演出。</p><p>本周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/31-per-cent-of-uk-nightclubs-closed-last-year-as-industry-demands-government-action-3587334">公布的统计数据显示，过去三年英国约 31% 的夜总会被迫关闭</a>。夜间产业协会呼吁政府立即采取行动应对危机，指出“夜总会行业深刻且系统性的边缘化”，这对“我们文化景观的活力”构成了威胁。</p><p> 1月份发布的另一份报告显示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/report-shows-disaster-facing-grassroots-music-venues-the-big-companies-and-arenas-are-now-going-to-have-to-answer-for-this-3576307">，2023年英国草根音乐场馆将遭遇“灾难”</a> ，要求对更大的场馆征收门票税以及更广泛的行业进行投资的呼声越来越高。报告指出，核心问题是能源价格飙升、房东提高地税金额、供应成本、营业费率、许可问题、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchester-night-day-cardiff-fuel-post-lockdown-noise-complaints-venues-3103934">噪音投诉</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-thank-help-gigs-return-2021-2842425">COVID-19 的持续冲击波</a>。</p><p>去年，音乐场馆信托基金<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-annual-report-government-action-arena-investment-frank-turner-talent-pipeline-3389434">在议会大厦提交了第一份年度报告，警告英国的草根演出空间正在“走向悬崖”，</a>除非政府采取紧急行动和新的大型场馆的投资。在发出严厉警告称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-to-lose-10-per-cent-of-grassroots-venues-in-2023-as-calls-grow-for-rest-of-industry-to-invest-3499727">英国将在 2023 年失去 10% 的草根音乐场馆后，</a> MVT 和该行业的其他人士在年底时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2023-was-worst-year-for-venue-closures-while-no-one-in-music-industry-seems-to-care-say-mvt-3562266">告诉<i>NME</i> 2023 年是“场馆关闭最糟糕的一年</a>”，而“没有人”音乐界似乎很关心”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pryzm-boss-blames-young-people-drinking-less-for-nightclub-closures-3588126">Pryzm 老板将夜总会关闭归咎于“年轻人少喝酒”，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《怪奇物语》明星将领衔布雷特·伊斯顿·埃利斯的导演处女作https://www.nme.com/news/film/stranger-things-star-lead-bret-easton-ellis-directorial-debut-3588134?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=stranger-things-star-lead-bret-伊斯顿·埃利斯导演处女作Alex BerryThu, 15 Feb 2024 21:31:35 +0000 Film NewsNewsMarvelStranger Things https://www.nme.com/?p=3588134 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="约瑟夫·奎因" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《美国精神病人》作者正在执导他的第一部故事片</p><p>布雷特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/stranger-things-star-lead-bret-easton-ellis-directorial-debut-3588134">·伊斯顿·埃利斯 (Bret Easton Ellis) 执导的《怪奇物语》后主演的导演处女作</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="约瑟夫·奎因" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Joseph-Quinn-relapse-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/stranger-things"><em>《怪奇物语》</em></a>主演约瑟夫·奎恩将出演一部名为<em>《复发》</em>的全新恐怖惊悚片。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/stranger-things-seaon-four-part-one-review-netflix-3232725">《怪奇物语》第四季第一部分评论：您所期待的所有恐怖刺激</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部电影将标志着作家布雷特·伊斯顿·埃利斯的导演处女作，他曾创作过<em>《美国精神病人》</em>和<em>《小于零》</em>等小说。</p><p>奎因将扮演马特·卡伦，一个年轻人，当他在一次聚会上目睹令人震惊的死亡事件时，他受庇护的生活被改变了。经过一段时间的康复治疗后，马特的病情似乎已经恢复稳定。然而，过去的阴影再次出现，他的问题变得更加严重。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/global/bret-easton-ellis-direct-relapse-joseph-quinn-1235909404/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，这部电影的剧情简介如下：“在马特不稳定的性格和社交媒体的入侵力量的推动下，马特的偏执与日俱增，扰乱了他的康复计划。当他再次开始使用时，一种神秘的存在开始在马特周围生长，而一个从他十几岁起就一直困扰着他的怪物显露出来。他的治疗师试图提供帮助，并确信这个怪物实际上就在马特的脑海里。” </p><figure id="attachment_3588138" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588138" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588138" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bret-Easton-Ellis.jpg" alt="布雷特·伊斯顿·埃利斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bret-Easton-Ellis.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bret-Easton-Ellis-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bret-Easton-Ellis-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bret-Easton-Ellis-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bret-Easton-Ellis-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bret-Easton-Ellis-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3588138" class="wp-caption-text">布雷特·伊斯顿·埃利斯 (Bret Easton Ellis) 于 2019 年 10 月 20 日在意大利罗马。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Vittorio Zunino Celotto/Getty Images for RFF</figcaption></figure><p>埃利斯告诉<em>《综艺》杂志</em>，他的导演处女作是一部恐怖片，这是“恰当的”。他说：“我是看着 20 世纪 70 年代的标志性恐怖电影长大的。我写了一本恐怖小说<i>《月球公园》</i> ，以向史蒂芬·金致敬。</p><p> “我的第一部长片是一部恐怖片似乎很合适。”</p><p>他继续描述这个项目说：“ <i>《Relapse》</i>有一种简单性，这似乎是我导演处女作的完美形式：直接而有影响力的东西。”</p><p>据<em>《综艺》</em>报道，他详细阐述了即将上映的电影：“这将给我带来冲击：性、毒品和偏执。这也将是一部有趣、丰富且商业化的故事片，适合很多人欣赏。”</p><p>奎因最近被曝将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pedro-pascal">佩德罗·帕斯卡</a>、凡妮莎·柯比和埃邦·莫斯-巴克拉赫一起加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel">漫威</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/marvel-fantastic-four-pedro-pascal-vanessa-kirby-cast-3587717">神奇四侠</a></em>的演员阵容。这位英国演员还将出演定于六月上映的 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/trailer-for-a-quiet-place-day-one-has-dropped-3584000"><em>《寂静之地：第一天》</em></a> 。</p><p>布雷特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/stranger-things-star-lead-bret-easton-ellis-directorial-debut-3588134">·伊斯顿·埃利斯 (Bret Easton Ellis) 执导的《怪奇物语》后主演的导演处女作</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
西尔维斯特·史泰龙希望瑞恩·高斯林成为下一个兰博https://www.nme.com/news/film/sylvester-stallone-wants-ryan-gosling-to-be-next-rambo-3588124?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sylvester-stallone-wants-ryan-gosling-下一个兰博Alex BerryThu, 15 Feb 2024 20:50:47 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3588124 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="史泰龙" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “如果我把接力棒传给他，我会把它传给他”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sylvester-stallone-wants-ryan-gosling-to-be-next-rambo-3588124">西尔维斯特·史泰龙希望瑞恩·高斯林成为下一个兰博的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="史泰龙" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sylvester-stallone">西尔维斯特·史泰龙</a>表示，他希望<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-gosling">瑞恩·高斯林</a>扮演下一个兰博。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>史泰龙在最近一集的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fTTa7gI1bqg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《今夜秀》</em></a>中透露，如果要重新审视该系列，他会将“接力棒”“传递”给他。</p><p>这位<em>《洛奇》</em>演员说：“我在一次晚宴上认识了[高斯林]。 [高斯林]说道，“我对<em>兰博</em>很着迷，我曾经打扮成兰博去学校，人们会赶我走，但我仍然没有停止。我会以兰博的身份去度假。他只是一直说他和<em>兰博</em>有很多联系。”</p><p> “我想，你知道，这很有趣。如果我把接力棒传给他，我会把它传给他，因为他喜欢这个角色，”他补充道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3588129" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588129" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588129" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo.jpg" alt="史泰龙" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Sylvester-Stallone-Rambo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3588129" class="wp-caption-text">西尔维斯特·史泰龙 (Sylvester Stallone) 出现在 1988 年电影《第一滴血 III》中的场景。图片来源：Getty/TriStar/Getty Images 摄</figcaption></figure><p>史泰龙在该系列的前四部电影中饰演约翰·兰博。原版电影《<em>第一滴血</em>》改编自同名小说，于 1982 年上映，成为全球票房第七高的电影。</p><p>他重申他会批准高斯林的选角，并表示：“我会同意，但我不知道是否有人会说，‘嘿，他长得太帅了，不适合扮演兰博。’”</p><p>这位演员在第一次见面时还说道：“显然我们是相反的。他长得很帅。我不是。严重地！你能把我想象成肯吗？这根本不起作用。”</p><p>高斯林因在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greta-gerwig">格蕾塔·葛韦格</a>的<em>《芭比娃娃》</em>中饰演肯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2024-nominations-rolling-list-3575357">而获得奥斯卡最佳男配角提名</a>。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/features/ryan-gosling-barbie-oscars-performance-snubs-ken-1235898750/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Variety》</em></a>报道，高斯林表示，史泰龙 1980 年代的着装为肯在电影中标志性的貂皮大衣提供了一些灵感。 </p><figure id="attachment_3588130" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588130" style="width: 1485px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588130" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ryan-Gosling-Rambo.jpg" alt="瑞恩·高斯林" width="1485" height="943" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ryan-Gosling-Rambo.jpg 1485w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ryan-Gosling-Rambo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ryan-Gosling-Rambo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ryan-Gosling-Rambo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ryan-Gosling-Rambo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Ryan-Gosling-Rambo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1485px) 100vw, 1485px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3588130" class="wp-caption-text">瑞恩·高斯林在《芭比娃娃》中饰演肯 (Ken) 图片来源：华纳兄弟影业</figcaption></figure><p>高斯林分享说，这有助于区分肯的多个角色：“我们发现史泰龙穿着很多貂皮。只要肯穿着它，他就是穿着貂皮的肯——这将他与其他肯家族区分开来。”</p><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sylvester-stallone-pays-tribute-to-carl-weathers-rest-in-power-and-keep-punching-3581840">史泰龙向他的前<em>《洛奇》</em>搭档卡尔·韦瑟斯致敬，卡尔·韦瑟斯</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/carl-weathers-star-of-rocky-predator-and-the-mandalorian-dies-at-76-3581491">于 2 月 1 日去世，享年 76 岁</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sylvester-stallone-wants-ryan-gosling-to-be-next-rambo-3588124">西尔维斯特·史泰龙希望瑞恩·高斯林成为下一个兰博的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
